ef subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCollection" target="L02267">Schnitzler an Beer-Hofmann, 23. 7. 1917</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCollection" target="L02269">Schnitzler an Adam, 27. 8. 1917</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L02264">Adam an Schnitzler, 19. 6. 1917</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L02269">Schnitzler an Adam, 27. 8. 1917</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
